    • Method Detail

      • execute

        public SimpleResult<org.springframework.data.domain.Page,com.google.common.collect.Multimap> execute()

        Override of the interface Command execute method. Checks if the user exists by user id.

        If user exists it will create a Page of class AppointmentInfo objects and return this in the SimpleResult.success value.

        If user does not exist, it will return the errors in a SimpleResult.error value with a null success

        See Also:
        interface Command, class AppointmentInfo
